    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Devices attached to a sash rail by which the window may be raised or lowered; may be flush-mounted cups or surface-mounted bars or hooks.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
